author: Ben Kesslen
title: At least two tornados hit central Texas as Louisiana faces severe weather
description: At least two tornados hit central Texas as Louisiana faces severe weather
content:
At least two tornadoes hit central Texas and severe windstorms whipped Louisiana on Sunday as both states battle coronavirus with stay-at-home orders.
